Dystribute is a new writing platform that will rely on 100% paid social marketing to promote articles and compensate writers for their original content via a revenue share with the platform. We are looking for the following criteria in our writers to become our beta testers:
 
1.     Solid writing experience especially in social/shareable media – published links will be requested
2.     1-5 years of writing experience in various full-time and freelance positions
3.     Understanding of social media marketing and content promotion
4.     Being a native English speaker is a must
5.     Willingness to be beta testers and partners for the platform
6.     Ability to dedicate 5-7 hours per week writing on a freelance basis and 1-2 hours a month for feedback sessions
 
There will be a revenue share in place for articles published. Beta writers will be compensated with a fixed fee in addition to this for their feedback and being early partners.
 






